{"tid":1152804,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[假人真事] 《我的極品室友》","createTime":"2019-05-13T08:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T12:38:24.000Z","uid":253440,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b56a67699d10f05c06dd0508200ed5d72d0c58a9","tid":1152804,"uid":253440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"是咁的 近呢半年以嚟 我一直係自己ig久唔久文字抱怨我同屋主嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢啲行為真係夠晒極品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全屋人都對佢有怨言<br />\n但係佢屢勸不改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我無聊畫出嚟諗住打發吓時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果好多人話比我聽好鍾意睇<br />\n仲收到大家嘅慰問同表示對極品感到無奈<br />\n以下我就開始分享我嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n((頭盔))無畫功可言<br />\n同埋因為準備緊FYP 所以update可能比較慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />內含粗口 會打冷震就上一頁<br />\n有興趣可以去ig睇：@haakmuidraws<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SeqzF2S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSeqzF2S.png&h=8b3d97b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac8ea07cad388a9d56b196279c1f8daca6b4effd","tid":1152804,"uid":253440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T08:25:53.000Z","msg":"EP 1 - 初遇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/at1vepd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fat1vepd.jpg&h=34f68cee&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2M8xsKc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2M8xsKc.jpg&h=acbe3241&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hx1i7Kc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhx1i7Kc.jpg&h=2654fb3b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gBa